text:
You would want to create a custom module for this then include it in the post template. Something like this in your module:
```
&lt;section style="background: url('{{module.imgSelectorField.src}}')  no-repeat center center/cover;"&gt;
	&lt;div class="title"&gt; {{content.title}}&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;div class="post-meta"&gt;{{content.auhtor.firstName}} and any other data you wanted to add&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;
```
